{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884492763,"sessionID":"ses_28509b942ffeo3dSThXccTyRCR","part":{"id":"prt_d7af6bd41001A9WGErgnFpyBxY","messageID":"msg_d7af6ab25001f7f1cPa7on2kQQ","sessionID":"ses_28509b942ffeo3dSThXccTyRCR","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_2f5bdd69dd314ac09b55b6e7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-041: E2E 集成测试\n\n## Summary\n\n为 AgentCube 项目编写端到端（E2E）集成测试，验证完整的功能流程和系统集成。\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nAgentCube 项目需要 E2E 集成测试来验证系统在真实环境下的行为，确保各组件之间的集成正确性。\n\n### Goal\n\n1. 搭建 E2E 测试框架和基础设施\n2. 覆盖核心功能场景\n3. 验证系统集成正确性\n\n### Value\n\n- 验证端到端功能正确性\n- 减少回归风险\n- 提高发布信心\n\n---\n\n## Scope\n\n### In-Scope\n\n- E2E 测试框架搭建\n- 核心功能场景测试\n- 测试数据管理\n- CI/CD 集成\n\n### Out-of-Scope\n\n- 单元测试（已有专门 AR）\n- 性能测试\n- 压力测试\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. E2E 测试框架就绪\n2. 核心场景测试覆盖\n3. 测试可通过 CI 执行\n4. 测试报告可读\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Scope Analysis\n\n### 待分析\n\n- 详细功能范围待确定\n- 测试用例待梳理\n- 依赖服务待明确\n\n---\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Benefits\n\n1. 验证完整功能流程\n2. 快速发现集成问题\n\n### Risks\n\n1. 测试环境依赖复杂\n2. 测试执行时间较长\n\n### Dependencies\n\n- 待确定\n\n### 预估工作量\n\n- Size: L（约 5+ 人日）\n- 待评估\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n1. **Phase 1**: 需求分析和技术选型\n2. **Phase 2**: 测试框架搭建\n3. **Phase 3**: 测试用例实现\n4. **Phase 4**: CI/CD 集成\n5. **Phase 5**: 测试维护和扩展\n\n---\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### 待补充\n\n---\n\n## Test Framework\n\n- **Framework**: Go testing\n- **执行**: `go test ./test/e2e/...`\n- **依赖**: 待确定","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-041/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-041/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-041/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775884492753,"end":1775884492761}}}